							     surgery only removes other AddedBodyPartBase hediffs (not plain
							     hediffs), Heyra_HornHediff is always present alongside biohorn
							     hediffs.  Being first in the list, it always matched first,
							     blocking all biohorn/dragon entries from ever being selected. -->
							<hediffGraphics>
